{"id": "7592", "post": "<div class=\"post-7592 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-brazil tag-chicago tag-exclusive tag-frankfurt tag-germany tag-host1plus-com tag-johannesburg tag-los-angeles tag-openvz tag-sao-paolo tag-south-africa tag-usa\" id=\"post-7592\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/host1plus-openvz-vps-in-brazil-south-africa-germany-usa-starting-at-2-50month/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Host1Plus \u2013 OpenVZ VPS in Brazil, South Africa, Germany, USA starting at $2.50/month</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/brazil/\" rel=\"tag\">brazil</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/chicago/\" rel=\"tag\">chicago</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/exclusive/\" rel=\"tag\">exclusive</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/frankfurt/\" rel=\"tag\">Frankfurt</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/germany/\" rel=\"tag\">germany</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/host1plus-com/\" rel=\"tag\">host1plus.com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/johannesburg/\" rel=\"tag\">johannesburg</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/los-angeles/\" rel=\"tag\">los angeles</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/openvz/\" rel=\"tag\">openvz</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/sao-paolo/\" rel=\"tag\">sao paolo</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/south-africa/\" rel=\"tag\">south africa</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/usa/\" rel=\"tag\">USA</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> September 4, 2015 @ 1:00 pm, by Jonathan Tan</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIzMDAiIGhlaWdodD0iMTkwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgMzAwIDE5MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Host1Plus-Web_Hosting_Services_Provided_by_HOST1PLUS_-_2014-07-19_17.28.30-300x190.png.webp\" alt=\"Host1Plus.com\" width=\"300\" height=\"190\"></a></p><p>Aurimas, from <a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Host1Plus.com,</a> sent us new offers for all the readers of LowEndBox to enjoy. These are available in four locations: USA (Chicago, Los Angeles), South Africa (Johannesburg), Brazil (S\u00e3o Paulo) and Germany (Frankfurt). There are two coupons available for this promotion.</p><p>The first promotion uses the coupon code <strong>SPLASH</strong> that gives a 40% discount for VPS plans with 1 to 6 month billing cycles. This can be used only once in all their four locations. Note that this is <strong>non-recurring</strong>, but the regular price still falls within the range of LEB prices. This coupon will end on September 15, 2015.</p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Bronze</strong><p></p><ul><li>256MB RAM</li><li>0.5 vCPU Core</li><li>20GB HDD space</li><li>500GB traffic</li><li>50Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>OpenVZ/Custom Control Panel</li><li>Coupon: <strong>SPLASH</strong></li><li><del>$2.50/month</del></li><li>$1.50/month</li><li><a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com/vps-hosting/\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Silver</strong><p></p><ul><li>768MB RAM</li><li>1 vCPU Core</li><li>30GB HDD space</li><li>1TB traffic</li><li>50Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>OpenVZ/Custom Control Panel</li><li>Coupon: <strong>SPLASH</strong></li><li><del>$5/month</del></li><li>$2/month</li><li><a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com/vps-hosting/\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><em>More offers inside!</em></p><p>The second promotion is targeted to their South Africa VPS hosting location using the coupon code <strong>VPSZA50</strong>. This promo code gives a 75% discount for VPS in this location with 1 to 12 month billing cycles. It can be used by new and existing customers more than once. This coupon is also <strong>non-recurring</strong> and can be used while supply last.</p><p><span id=\"more-7592\"></span></p><table><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Bronze</strong><p></p><ul><li>256MB RAM</li><li>0.5 vCPU Core</li><li>20GB HDD space</li><li>500GB traffic</li><li>50Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>OpenVZ/Custom Control Panel</li><li>Coupon: <strong>VPSZA75</strong></li><li><del>$3/month</del></li><li>$0.62/month</li><li><a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com/vps-hosting/\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Silver</strong><p></p><ul><li>768MB RAM</li><li>1 vCPU Core</li><li>30GB HDD space</li><li>1TB traffic</li><li>50Mbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4</li><li>OpenVZ/Custom Control Panel</li><li>Coupon: <strong>VPSZA75</strong></li><li><del>$6.50/month</del></li><li>$1.62/month</li><li><a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com/vps-hosting/\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p>For those interested with host node information. In Los Angeles, they are using Intel E5-2650 V2 and E5-2640 V2 on a 1Gbit shared network. In Chicago, they have Intel E5-2620 v3 on a 10Gbit shared network. For Brazil, they are using Intel E5-2440 on a 1Gbit shared network. And lastly, their Germany location uses L5630 on a 1Gbit shared network.</p><p>Host1Plus has been doing business since 2008 and is a division of D. E. Technologies Ltd., which is a registered company in England and Wales. They have offices in London (UK), Kaunas (Lithuania), Frankfurt am Maine (Germany), and Sao Paolo (Brazil). They have been featured here <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/host1plus-com/\">multiple times</a> already, and their <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/host1plus-1-5month-256mb-openvz-in-brazil-south-africa-germany-or-the-usa/\">last post</a> has generated a good amount of interest.</p><p>Aurimas also told us some exciting addition to their service. <a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com/press/host1plus-launches-ddos-protection/\">DDoS protection</a> (Staminus) is now available in their USA, Brazil and South Africa locations. They have now implemented <a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com/blog/tutorials/host1plus-implements-dns-management/\">DNS management</a>. <a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com/press/host1plus-application-installer/\">1-Click Installer</a> is now available that can be used to install WordPress, OpenVPN, ISPConfig, and cPanel. You can select applications to install at the checkout. Lastly, they have updated their <a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com/blog/articles/host1plus-renews-the-client-area/\">dashboard / client area</a>.</p><p>Supported payment methods includes Debit/Credit card, PayPal, AliPay, WebMoney, Skrill, CashU, Ebanx and Paysera. Some of the prohibited activities are: use of copyright infringing content, UDP flood, DoS type activities and Email spam. Gaming, teamspeak servers, proxies are allowed. Kindly read their <a href=\"http://www.host1plus.com/terms-of-service/\">Terms of Service</a> carefully before making any purchase.</p><p><strong>Network information</strong></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Frankfurt am Main, Germany</span><br>\nIPv4 test: 5.175.192.201</p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">S\u00e3o Paulo, Brazil</span><br>\nIPv4 test: 181.41.197.5</p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span class=\"vps_loc_tab active\"><span class=\"loc_text\">Johannesburg, South Africa</span></span></span><br>\nIPv4 test: 154.127.61.2</p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span class=\"vps_loc_tab\"><span class=\"loc_text\">Chicago IL, USA</span></span></span><br>\nIPv4 test: 191.101.1.2</p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Los 